Technology stack:
Laravel
PHP 7.x
WeatherApi is a Laravel 8.x project that uses real-time weather detection.
It uses the Free Weather API (http://api.weatherapi.com).
Implementation:
You need to create your own account (http://api.weatherapi.com) to get a key then insert it in "WeatherController"
to get the forecast for a city.
Git clone cmd > git clone https://github.com/minnieninnie/weatherApi.git
Composer update cmd > composer update
